reviewText: Here again is a great movie.  It's partner movie One, Two Go is also great.  Love the old 747-100/200's 2 thumbs up for this one.

This presentation gives great views and narrative of the "queen of the skies" great 747 classic. These airplanes simply aren't around anymore and what a way to preserve the public's appreciation for this grand ole' lady of an aircraft through yet another stellar dvd produced by Just Planes!
